        "custom_liquid": "{% comment %}\nImage with Text Module\n- This code is used to display an image with accompanying text.\n- Replace the image URL, heading, and paragraph content with your desired content.\n{% endcomment %}\n\n<div class=\"row product-tabs-content js-product-tabs-content-detail\">\n  <div class=\"small-12 columns\">\n    <div class=\"image-with-text column-spacing-- grid--image-medium text_first text-left section-spacing section-spacing--disable-top section-spacing--disable-bottom\" style=\"--color-bg:#ffffff;--color-text:#2c2d2e;--color-text-rgb: 44,45,46; --solid-button-background: #2c2d2e; --solid-button-background-hover: #1b1b1c; --solid-button-label: #ffffff;--bg-body: #ffffff;--color-border: #e2e2e2\">\n      <div class=\"image-with-text--image image-with-text--inner\">\n        <div class=\"image-with-text--image-media aspect-ratio aspect-ratio--adapt\" style=\"--ratio-percent: 100.0%;\">\n          <img class=\"no-blur lazyautosizes ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" data-sizes=\"auto\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0747/3440/3866/files/11.webp?v=1708677945\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0747/3440/3866/files/11.webp?v=1708677945\" alt=\"Ample Space Image\" style=\"object-position: 50.0% 50.0%;\" sizes=\"406px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0747/3440/3866/files/11.webp?v=1708677945\">\n          <noscript>\n            <img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" sizes=\"auto\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0747/3440/3866/files/11.webp?v=1708677945\" alt=\"Ample Space Image\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"object-position: 50.0% 50.0%;\" />\n          </noscript>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"image-with-text--content image-with-text--inner\">\n        <div class=\"image-with-text--content--inner\">\n          <h3 class=\"h3\">Ample Space</h3>\n          <div class=\"rte\">\n            <p>\n              The anymaka hammock is roomy enough to accommodate 2-3 people with full-body support. (Unpacked dimensions: 141*86 in/358*220 cm).\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
      }
